{"tid":541963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[tvb不會敢報導] 青島往杭州高鐵車廂起火","createTime":"2018-01-27T04:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T08:27:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f680154d4826176808c2601beafdcef748906dce","tid":541963,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"【短片】青島往杭州高鐵車廂起火　200旅客滯留 (16:23)<br />\n2018/1/25<br />\n<br />\n 共1幅  上一頁下一頁 <br />\n據中鐵上海局官方微博「上鐵資訊」顯示，今午11時53分一列由青島往杭州高鐵，駛經安徽定遠站時，車廂電器設備發生故障起火。現時，當局已撲熄火警，並疏散民眾，無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n起火車廂是G281次列車2號車廂。據目擊者表示，當時由乘務員通知乘客疏散，而事發後至少200名旅客滯留在定遠站候車大廳，眾人情緒穩定。現時當局啟動應急預案，開始統計各名滯留旅客目的地，並調查事故原因。"},{"pid":"8052f4d161951e11759f7c9fab154c94fabb77af","tid":541963,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180125/s00004/bbb1365eba4823098c9d8caf0c7f4eb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180125%2Fs00004%2Fbbb1365eba4823098c9d8caf0c7f4eb6.jpg&h=8a8e4335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"244b222e4d29b7a663d6d8c26de26d596b7699ce","tid":541963,"uid":39872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"CCTVB係駐美日機構<br />\n日撚日凈係美日新聞<br />\n今朝又話美國咩流感<br />\n而我凈係知道SARS係支那傳入殺害香港市民"},{"pid":"8f46819e630978c863b5c83fdbe808bae1f5e7f4","tid":541963,"uid":4302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> tvb"},{"pid":"da5530f746fce820b2bad433d5dac225e26c52f1","tid":541963,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"直達地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f048d269b718bcc72273a95ebaee1d89c2b8903","tid":541963,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-